  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e50f79245aa9f924b95c8133ed43f8dc, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InteractableObject
  title: Richelieu Pavyonu
  description: "Louvre'un kuzey kanad\u0131 olan Richelieu Pavyonu, ad\u0131n\u0131
    Kardinal Richelieu'den al\u0131r. 1993 y\u0131l\u0131nda Maliye Bakanl\u0131\u011F\u0131'n\u0131n
    bu binadan ta\u015F\u0131nmas\u0131yla m\xFCzeye kat\u0131lm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r.\r\n\r\nMimari
    \xF6zellikler:\r\n- 3 b\xFCy\xFCk cam \xE7at\u0131l\u0131 i\xE7 avlu (Marly,
    Puget, Khorsabad)\r\n- Napolyon III'\xFCn muhte\u015Fem dairelerin yer ald\u0131\u011F\u0131
    kat\r\n- I. M. Pei'nin tasarlad\u0131\u011F\u0131 modern d\xFCzenleme\r\n\r\nKoleksiyonlar:\r\n-
    Frans\u0131z Resmi (14.-19. y\xFCzy\u0131l)\r\n- Kuzey Avrupa Resmi (Flaman,
    Hollandal\u0131, Alman)\r\n- \u0130slam Sanatlar\u0131 (yeni galeri, 2012)\r\n-
    Frans\u0131z Heykelleri ve Dekoratif Sanatlar\r\n- Mezopotamya antikalar\u0131
    (Khorsabad galerisi)"
  imageOptional: {fileID: 0}
  highlightOnHover: 1
  highlightColor: {r: 1, g: 0.85, b: 0.4, a: 1}
